metadata.description:
Welcome to hedsTAPE 13. For this cycle, we've curated a hybrid vocal & production sample from the trailblazing web3 artist Reo Cragun. Crafted with the same passion and innovation that defined Reo's ascent in the music world, this unique recording is a cornerstone of sonic creativity. The sample's dynamic composition ensures a captivating experience, while spiraling harmonic chops deliver unparalleled tonal balance. Flip Reo's sample and enter the world of creative collaboration.

    This hedsTAPE was curated by Reo Cragun during a collaborative production cycle. Each track is accompanied by a visualizer, and the entire mix is included with each mint. The talented artists featured in this mix have been chosen anonymously via heds community curation, and appear in the following order:
    
    rage logic
    envi
    Fresh Stuff
    glasstempo
    george hooks
    allove
    robu
    vaarwell
    Pala Chrome
    billings
    
    Find out how to participate @ heds.app
metadata.name: hedsTAPE 13 #1
